{"tid":1517551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共新奸計: 建立無形大台。","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T03:12:50.000Z","uid":62011,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca312d17aeaf7a1794a711cbdd35a073f65079d1","tid":1517551,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:46.000Z","msg":"又拉G PHONG，又拉周庭，又拉陳天浩。<br />\n其實呢班人係反送中入面幾乎無咩角色/領導。<br />\n港共偏偏呢個時候拉佢，仲要唔知咩罪名塔佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家小心被引導，將佢地視為領袖，被代表。重演928</span></strong><br />\n我好同情三位，但委屈下你地先。<br />\n<br />\n繼續流水社運:<br />\n一、無名無姓。沒行動組織，蒙面，不接受採訪，不公開談論，不留下秘密談論的記錄或痕跡。<br />\n二、不言不語。不發言，不公開訴求，不寫大字報。<br />\n三、聚散無踪。不長期佔領，隨時解散，隨時聚合，行動的後續不定。<br />\n<br />\n行動原則:<br />\n1：五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n2：兄弟爬山，各自努力，齊上齊落。<br />\n3：不割席，不指責，不篤灰。<br />\n4：沒有大台/領導人物。<br />\n<br />\n借力打力: 向外媒宣揚呢件事，表達港共不惜一切打壓示威者。"},{"pid":"517f479299e8d216edde7480fbcc3232c921f8e0","tid":1517551,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=06e4f9de\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=6fe4ac72\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=98e441b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid"